Rod Cameron (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rod_Cameron_(actor) 0 Rod Cameron (born Nathan Roderick Cox, December 7, 1910 – December 21, 1983) was a Canadian-born film and television actor whose career extended from the 1930s to the 1970s. He appeared in horror, war, action and science fiction movies, but is best remembered for his many westerns.
